              "label": "B",
              "text": "The proof is completely correct, but there are counterexamples to the claim."
            },
            {
              "label": "C",
              "text": "The proof is wrong, and the first error occurs on line I."
            },
            {
              "label": "D",
              "text": "The proof is wrong, and the first error occurs on line II."
            },
            {
              "label": "E",
              "text": "The proof is wrong, and the first error occurs on line III."
            },
            {
              "label": "F",
              "text": "The proof is wrong, and the first error occurs on line IV."
            },
            {
              "label": "G",
              "text": "The proof is wrong, and the first error occurs on line V."
            }
